  <steps>
    <step order="0">Context check: working tree clean, branch `work/ai-spaarke-action-engine-r1`, baseline build passes. Task 030 ✅ (need `GateRequest` field names + `GateType` enum for the props contract). Task 032 in flight OR ✅ — read `notes/decisions/032-sse-gate-events.md` for the SSE event shape if available; otherwise coordinate the contract here and feed back. Load knowledge. Declare RIGOR LEVEL: FULL.</step>
    <step order="1">Create folder `src/client/shared/Spaarke.UI.Components/src/components/GateApprovalCard/`.</step>
    <step order="2">Create `GateApprovalCard.types.ts` — export `GateCardProps` interface mirroring server-side `GateRequest` field names (camelCase TS): `correlationId`, `gateType` (string union mirroring 5-value enum), `summary`, `payloadPreview?: string`, `authorizedApproverRoles: string[]`, `surfaceHint?: string`, `timeoutSeconds: number`, `requestedByDisplayName: string`, `requestedAtUtc: string`. Export `GateApprovalCardProps = { gateRequest: GateCardProps; onApprove: () =&gt; void | Promise&lt;void&gt;; onReject: (reason: string) =&gt; void | Promise&lt;void&gt;; disabled?: boolean; className?: string; }`.</step>
    <step order="3">Create `GateApprovalCard.styles.ts` — `makeStyles` with semantic tokens (`tokens.colorNeutralBackground1`, `tokens.colorNeutralForeground1`, `tokens.colorBrandBackground`, `tokens.colorPaletteRedBackground1` for urgency border &lt;60 sec, etc.). NO hardcoded hex/rgb. Define `card`, `header`, `body`, `footer`, `urgencyBorder`, `timer`, `actions`, `rejectionReasonInput` classes.</step>
    <step order="4">Create `GateApprovalCard.tsx`:
      - Functional component using `useState` for countdown + reject-reason input visibility + reject reason text.
      - `useEffect` for countdown ticker (decrement every 1 sec; pure visual).
      - Layout: `Card` from `@fluentui/react-components` with header (gate-type Badge + summary), body (payloadPreview in `pre` block, authorizedApproverRoles list), footer (timer + Approve `Button` primary + Reject `Button` secondary).
      - Reject click opens inline `Textarea` + Cancel/Submit; Submit calls `onReject(reason)`.
      - Approve click calls `onApprove()` and disables both buttons (prevent double-submit).
      - Accessibility: ARIA labels on buttons, `role="region"` + `aria-label` on the Card, focus management when reject-reason opens.</step>
    <step order="5">Create `index.ts` — `export * from './GateApprovalCard'; export type * from './GateApprovalCard.types';`. Update `src/client/shared/Spaarke.UI.Components/src/index.ts` to re-export `GateApprovalCard`.</step>
    <step order="6">Create `GateApprovalCard.test.tsx` — Jest + React Testing Library tests:
      (a) Renders with all required props.
      (b) Countdown ticker decrements.
      (c) Approve click invokes `onApprove` and disables buttons.
      (d) Reject click reveals reason input.
      (e) Submit reject invokes `onReject(reason)` with the entered text.
      (f) Cancel reject hides reason input.
      (g) `disabled` prop disables both buttons + hides reason input.
      (h) Accessibility: `Card` has `aria-label`; buttons have descriptive labels.
      (i) Snapshot test (light theme).
      (j) Snapshot test (dark theme — render under `&lt;FluentProvider theme={webDarkTheme}&gt;`).</step>
    <step order="7">Build the package: `npm run build` in `src/client/shared/Spaarke.UI.Components/`. Run tests: `npm test`. All pass.</step>
    <step order="8">If Storybook exists in the package, add a story file `GateApprovalCard.stories.tsx` with 4 variants: Default, NearTimeout (10 sec remaining), DarkMode, Disabled. Verify visually under Storybook (optional but recommended).</step>
    <step order="9">Bundle-size impact: `Spaarke.UI.Components` has a per-component budget tracked in the package's CI step (check `package.json` build scripts). Verify added bundle delta is small (target: &lt; 20 KB minified-gzipped).</step>
    <step order="9.5">Run quality gates: `code-review` (Fluent v9 semantic-token correctness, accessibility, no hardcoded colors, props contract matches `GateRequest` server-side, type safety), `adr-check` (ADR-006/011/012/021).</step>
    <step order="9.7">Run `ui-test` skill against deployed SpaarkeAi (after Phase 5 task 050 mounts the card). For Phase 3, the UI tests below describe the targets; full execution happens during integration testing in Phase 6 task 062.</step>
    <step order="10">Update `tasks/TASK-INDEX.md`: 036 ✅. Update `current-task.md`. Phase 3 complete after Group D + 035 + 036 all ✅.</step>
    <step order="11">Commit + push. Note the props contract finalization in `notes/decisions/036-gateapprovalcard-props-contract.md` so Phase 5 task 050 (SpaarkeAi card-mount) consumes the stable shape.</step>
  </steps>

  <ui-tests>
    <test name="Component Renders">
      <url>https://{org}.crm.dynamics.com/main.aspx?appid={app-id}&amp;pagetype=control&amp;controlName=sprk_spaarkeai</url>
      <steps>
        <step>Navigate to SpaarkeAi Code Page</step>
        <step>Trigger a gate-required Action (e.g., "Send weekly task digest" with humanGate=true)</step>
        <step>Verify `GateApprovalCard` renders with gate type, summary, payloadPreview, countdown timer, Approve + Reject buttons</step>
        <step>Check browser console for JavaScript errors</step>
      </steps>
      <expected>Card renders without console errors; all props (gateType, summary, payloadPreview, authorizedApproverRoles, countdown) visible</expected>
    </test>
    <test name="Dark Mode Compliance (ADR-021)">
      <url>https://{org}.crm.dynamics.com/main.aspx?appid={app-id}&amp;pagetype=control&amp;controlName=sprk_spaarkeai</url>
      <steps>
        <step>Open SpaarkeAi with `GateApprovalCard` visible (gate-required Action triggered)</step>
        <step>Toggle Dataverse app to dark theme (or use OS dark mode if app respects system theme)</step>
        <step>Verify card background, text, borders, and button colors all shift to dark-theme palette</step>
        <step>Inspect computed styles — assert NO hardcoded hex/rgb values; all colors resolve to Fluent v9 semantic tokens</step>
        <step>Toggle back to light theme — verify symmetric correctness</step>
        <step>Check console for any theme-related warnings</step>
      </steps>
      <expected>Card visually correct under both light and dark themes; no hardcoded colors; semantic tokens used throughout; no console warnings</expected>
    </test>
    <test name="User Interaction">
      <url>https://{org}.crm.dynamics.com/main.aspx?appid={app-id}&amp;pagetype=control&amp;controlName=sprk_spaarkeai</url>
      <steps>
        <step>Trigger a gate-required Action; `GateApprovalCard` renders</step>
        <step>Click Approve button — verify loading indicator appears + buttons disable</step>
        <step>Verify the Action proceeds (chat shows next step or final result)</step>
        <step>Trigger a second gate; click Reject button</step>
        <step>Verify inline Textarea appears for rejection reason</step>
        <step>Enter reason "test rejection" and click Submit</step>
        <step>Verify the Action terminates with the rejection reason in chat history</step>
        <step>Verify audit log entry contains the rejection reason (admin check)</step>
      </steps>
      <expected>Approve submits and progresses Action; Reject reveals reason input, accepts text, terminates Action with reason; both within 3 seconds; no double-submit</expected>
    </test>
  </ui-tests>

  <tools>
