    <criterion testable="true">10 Jest tests pass: render, countdown, approve-click, reject-click, reject-submit, reject-cancel, disabled, accessibility, light-snapshot, dark-snapshot.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">`GateApprovalCard` exported from `@spaarke/ui-components` top-level; consumers can `import { GateApprovalCard, GateCardProps }` from the package.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Zero hardcoded color values in `GateApprovalCard.styles.ts` and `GateApprovalCard.tsx` — verified by grep for `#[0-9a-f]{3,8}|rgb\(`.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Dark-mode test passes: rendering under `webDarkTheme` produces a distinct, correct visual output (snapshot diff).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Bundle-size delta &lt; 20 KB minified-gzipped (target).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">UI tests defined in `&lt;ui-tests&gt;` section: Component Renders, Dark Mode Compliance (ADR-021), User Interaction. Each ready for `ui-test` skill execution in Phase 6 task 062.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Props contract documented in `notes/decisions/036-gateapprovalcard-props-contract.md` for Phase 5 task 050 to consume.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">`code-review` + `adr-check` pass at Step 9.5; ADR-006/011/012/021 cited in PR description.</criterion>
